name: Sugar Cookies
description: Versatile sugar cookie dough is like edible modeling clay. It can be simply rolled into balls and baked, like snickerdoodles, but when you want to take it further and cut sugar cookie into shapes, like The Best Rolled Sugar Cookies, these tips will help your sugar cookie cut-outs turn out beautifully every time.
author: Diane Cash

name: Thick Cut-Outs
description: A big batch of big thick sugar cookies. These are THE big soft sugar cookies you have been looking for. Frost them while warm and sprinkle with colored sugar.
author: Jennifer Schmidt

name: Chicken Pot Pie IX
description: A delicious chicken pot pie made from scratch with carrots, peas, and celery for a comfort…
author: Dilyara Garifullina

name: Ginger-Chicken Stir Fry
description: Stir fries require very little cooking time and you can pretty much use any vegetables you like, but the star of this one is the ginger. This dish is quick and easy to make, but get all of your ingredients together (including mixing the sauce) before you start cooking because everything happens fast! Serve with rice, and garnish with sliced green onions.
author: Sam Moqadam

name: Air Fryer Keto Chicken Wings
description: These air-fried chicken wings are finished in under 15 minutes and a great dish if you are on the keto diet. If desired, separate wings into drumettes.
author: Atharva Tulsi

name: Chicken Fajita Cauliflower Pizza
description: All your favorite chicken fajita flavors on a delicious, better-for-you cauliflower pizza crust!
author: Chad Montano

name: Margherita Pizza with Sausage and Pesto
description: Two of my favorite ingredients, pesto sauce and sausage, come together to make one of my family's favorite foods: pizza! They loved how crispy, melty, and cheesy it was! Feel free to adjust ingredients according to your personal tastes.
author: Karthik Garikapati

name: Taco Salad Pizza
description: When you can't decide between pizza and tacos, make both! Save time by starting with a pre-made frozen CAULIPOWER® crust.
author: Taylor Kiser

name: Southern Chicken Burrito
description: Your standard chicken burrito with a southern twist
author: Johnny Cash

name: Chicken Salad
description: just your average chicken salad passing through.
author: Anh Nguyen
